      • getParserFacade

        public PsiJavaParserFacade getParserFacade()
        Description copied from class: JavaPsiFacade
        Returns the factory for the project, which can be used to create instances of certain Java constructs from their textual representation. Elements created shall not be used to later intermix (like insert into) a PSI parsed from the user codebase since no formatting to the user code style will be performed in this case. Please use JavaPsiFacade.getElementFactory() instead, which provides exactly same methods but ensures created instances will get properly formatted.
        Specified by:
        getParserFacade in class JavaPsiFacade
        Returns:
        the parser facade.
